  "title": "Insurance Admin Executive (Motor Vehicle) – 1-Year Contract | 0580",
  "description": "<ul><li>Mondays to Thursday: 9am to 6.15pm</li><li>Fridays: 9am to 6pm</li><li>One Saturday per month: 9am to 1pm</li></ul><p><strong>Location:</strong> Alexandra Rd</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist Insurance Department with administrative duties on motor and general insurance.</li><li>Liaise with insurance companies and internal/external customers with regards to new/renewal quotations and issuance.</li><li>Proper updating of transactions into system accurately and keeping up-to-date records.</li><li>Compliance with industry practice for documentation and records. 5. Handles motor insurance sales.</li><li>Manage emails and phone inquiries from customers and internal stakeholders.</li><li>Coordinate to process insurance documentation.</li><li>Display ethical conduct and practice in all business dealings.</li><li>Maintain high service standards and accuracy in policy documentation.</li><li>Ensure requirements of the customer and the company are met.</li><li>Any other adhoc duties as and when assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least 2 years of working experience in a related field</li><li>Candidates with a Certificate in General Insurance (BCP, ComGi, PGI) will have an added advantage.</li></ul><p><br />The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd || 14C7279</p><p>Chua Jie Ying (Cai Jie Ying), Evelynn || EA Personnel License R24120580</p>",
